    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You are familiar with the latest and most cutting edge magitek weaponry, and are trained in its use. You gain access to the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.oUaeLZLK7WfolqBb]{Axe Musket}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.10J0WjnfgRvriLXc]{Gun Sword}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.zHJEzmoybIfX1LaV]{Hammer Gun}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.LDHGjtQHRM8bA8ZZ]{Rapier Pistol}. You have familiarity with weapons with the aforementioned weapons, plus bombs and firearms - for the purposes of proficiency, you treat any of these that are martial weapons as simple weapons and any that are advanced weapons as martial weapons.</p><p>At 5th level, whenever you get a critical hit with one of these weapons, you get its critical specialization effect.</p><p>At 9th level, you gain access to all uncommon combination weapons for which you meet the other requirements to use, and are familiar with all of them.</p>",
